    pricingDetail: `2026 pricing: Lite ($129/mo, 1 user, 5 projects, 10K keywords) includes core crawlers, keyword explorer, and rank tracking; Standard ($299/mo, 1 user, 10 projects, 20K keywords, 50K crawled pages) adds AI intent clustering, SERP volatility modeling, and Content Gap AI; Advanced ($599/mo, up to 3 users, 20 projects, 50K keywords, 100K crawled pages) unlocks AI workflow automations and custom reports; Enterprise AI ($999+/mo, custom users/projects) includes custom model training, API priority access, and dedicated infrastructure. Annual billing saves 20%.`,
